quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  19,76,"Sano Allah ni akwajonjechesyaga chongoko ŵandu ŵaajongweche, soni masengo gambone gakwendelechela ni gagali gambone nnope kwa Ambuje ŵenu pa malipilo, soni ni kwakuujila kwambone (ngaŵa ya duniya yaakutwanjila achimakafiliyo)."
  19,77,"Ana mum’bweni ajula jwaagakaaniile ma Ȃya Getu, ni kuŵecheta kuti: “Chisimu chene une (naga kumbuchisya soni ku umi pa Kiyama), chinjipedwa (soni) chipanje ni ŵanache (yaatite pakuumba pa duniya pano).”"
  19,78,"Ana jutekuilingula yakusisika, kapena jutaŵene chilanga ni (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji?"
  20,58,"“Chisimu nowe ŵakwe chitum’bichilile ni usaŵi wanti mpela uwwuwu, basi ŵiikaani chilikati chetuwe nomwe chilanga (chansongangano) changaŵa nkuchikulusya uwwe kapena mmwe, (chitusimanganile) pamalo pakuŵajilwa.”"
  20,59,"(Musa) jwatite: “Chilanga chenu (chiŵe) lisiku lyakulipeta (lyuŵa lyaung’ando), ni tasonganganyisidwe ŵandu ndaŵi jakwela nsana.”"
  20,60,"Basi Firiauna jwagalawiche ni kuja kusonganganya matipwi gakwe, kaneka jwaiche (ni asaŵi lisiku lyachilanga)."
  21,34,"Soni nganitum’bicheje mundu jwalijose paujo penu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) kuŵa jwandamo, ana naga mmwe kuwa, ŵanganyao nichaŵe ŵandamo?"
  21,35,"Ntima uliose uchipasya chiwa, ni tukun’dingaga ni yakusakala nambo soni ni yambone kuŵa mayeso (gakun’dinjila kupilila kwenu ni kutogolela kwenu), soni Kukwetu tinchiuchisyidwa."
  21,36,"Soni pati am’bweni mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) aŵala ŵakanile, ngaakuntendelaga inepe ikaŵeje chipongwe (pakuŵecheta kuti): “Ana aju ni jwaakwakolanga achimilungu ŵenu (mwachalu)?” Kutendaga ŵanganyao yakunkolanga (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji ŵanyao akukana."
  22,10,"(Chijukasalilidwe yanti): Yalakweyi ni ligongo lya ayila yagalongwesye makono genu, nambo soni kuti Allah nganaŵa jwakwatenda lupuso ata panandi achikapolo (Ŵakwe)."
  22,11,"Soni chilikati cha ŵandu pana jwaakun’galagatilaga Allah chanchisegambali (mwakayichila), basi naga yimpatile yambone, jukasatulalila nayo (ni kuŵa mpela nsilamu nsyesyene), nambo naga gampatile masausyo, jukasagalauka ni ngope jakwe (jukasaujilaga ku ukafili wakwe), jupelelwe duniya ni Akhera, kwalakweko ni kupelelwa kwakuonechela."
  22,12,"Jukasaŵaŵendaga, mmalo mwa Allah, aŵala ŵangaŵa nkumpa masausyo (naga nganiŵagalagatila), nambo soni ŵangaŵa nkumpa ikamuchisyo (naga ŵagalagatile), kwalakweko ni kupotela kwakutalikangana nnope (ni yakuona)."